AC_Warmachine.Tent_Upg_3_Description:
{~r}%Z-1 Upgrade{~}


												With this upgrade your creatures have to pay you gold for every healing they receive during combat. The amount of healing is muliplied by 5. The gold is added to your personal stash after combat.
												Although this upgrade is not entirely legal in Erathia, I still recommend buying it. Most creatures are too stupid and have no idea about laws and their rights, but with some you have to be careful not to take too much from them, be careful with Dwarves, Monks but also some others. If a lawsuit should arise, I will deny that I installed this upgrade for you.

